A long time has passed since I uploaded a horror theme! This one is my own extended version of "Someone Playing Piano", which is a simple but haunting musical score composed by Samuel Laflamme featured in the survival horror video game 'Outlast'. It is creepily played by a Variant, in a closed off backstage hallway, when Miles returns to the Administration Block.

I took the idea of working on this video after watching Piano Horror's video, so credits to him:
► https://youtu.be/iqNVIpVpT60

► Piano: Yamaha p-155b.
► Edition: Sony Vegas Pro 18.0.
► Composer: Samuel Laflamme.
